---
journal: {{ issue.journal_abbrev }}
journal_full: {{ issue.journal_full }}
volume: {{ issue.volume }}
issue: {{ issue.issue }}
publication_date: {{ issue.publication_date }}
fetched_at: {{ fetched_at }}
issue_url: {{ issue.issue_url }}
article_count: {{ issue.articles | length }}
oa_count: {{ issue.oa_count }}
---

# {{ issue.journal_abbrev }} — Vol {{ issue.volume }}, Issue {{ issue.issue }}

📅 出刊 {{ issue.publication_date }} · 抓取 {{ fetched_at }} · {{ issue.articles | length }} 篇文章{% if issue.oa_count %} ({{ issue.oa_count }} 篇 OA 🔓){% endif %}

> 在 Obsidian 勾選 ☑ 想要全文的；醫院 PC 請開 `{{ issue.filename_stem }}.html` 直接點 PDF 下載。

---
{% for article in issue.articles %}
## {{ loop.index }}. {{ article.title }}{% if article.is_open_access %} 🔓{% endif %}
{% if article.ai_analysis %}
> [!{% if article.ai_analysis.action == "必讀" %}danger{% elif article.ai_analysis.action == "瀏覽" %}tip{% else %}note{% endif %}] 🤖 AI 評析 — {{ article.ai_analysis.stars_emoji }} {{ article.ai_analysis.action }}
> {{ article.ai_analysis.body | replace('\n', '\n> ') }}
{% endif %}

- [ ] **要全文 PDF**

{% if article.authors %}**Authors**: {{ article.authors }}  {% endif %}
{% if article.article_type or article.pages %}{% if article.article_type %}**Type**: {{ article.article_type }}{% endif %}{% if article.article_type and article.pages %} · {% endif %}{% if article.pages %}**Pages**: {{ article.pages }}{% endif %}  {% endif %}
**DOI**: [{{ article.doi }}](https://doi.org/{{ article.doi }})
**原文**: [{{ article.article_url }}]({{ article.article_url }})

{% for header, body in article.abstract_sections %}
{% if header %}**{{ header }}.** {% endif %}{{ body }}
{% endfor %}
{% if not article.abstract_sections %}_（abstract 抓取失敗，請點 DOI 連結看原文）_
{% endif %}
---
{% endfor %}
